## Context

We are adding a new `next/geo` public entry point to the Next.js framework that provides geolocation helpers for middleware and edge functions. This follows the exact same pattern used by `next/server` to expose `userAgent`/`userAgentFromString` (via `server.js`, `server.d.ts`, and `src/server/web/spec-extension/user-agent.ts`). No existing code is modified except a two-line addition to the `files` array in `package.json`.

